## ðŸŽ¯ Key Patterns to Remember

| Keyword in Question     | Think                   |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------- |
| Options / Work packages | Phase E                 |
| Timeline / Sequencing   | Phase F                 |
| Compliance / Deviation  | Phase G                 |
| Change / Impact         | Phase H                 |
| New requirement         | Requirements Management |

